== 戊午の月 ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月}} is designated as the Bokugo {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種}} until the day before {{ill|Slightly Hot|ja|小暑}}) as applicable.

== 戊午の日 ==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu}} for Bokugo is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
Bokugo day is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専}}.



