== 戊午の月 ==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|May|ja|5月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} is designated as the Bokugo {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from {{ill|Mangzhong|ja|芒種|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Slightly Hot|ja|小暑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}) as applicable.

== 戊午の日 ==
The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} for Bokugo is as follows.
=== Selected Day (選日) ===
Bokugo day is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}}.
