==Pronunciation== ==Years of Yang Earth Horse== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 58 when divided by 60 is a year of Bokugo ([[:en:Year|year]]). {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Bokugo (戊午の年)''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 58|58 AD]] * [[:en:AD 118|118 AD]] * [[:en:178|178 AD]] * [[:en:238|238 AD]] * [[:en:298|298 AD]] * [[:en:358|358 AD]] * [[:en:418|418 AD]] * [[:en:478|478 AD]] * [[:en:538|538 AD]] * [[:en:598|598 AD]] * [[:en:658|658 AD]] * [[:en:718|718 AD]] * [[:en:778|778 AD]] * [[:en:838|838 AD]] * [[:en:898|898 AD]] * [[:en:958|958 AD]] | * [[:en:1018|1018 AD]] * [[:en:1078|1078 AD]] * [[:en:1138|1138 AD]] * [[:en:1198|1198 AD]] * [[:en:1258|1258 AD]] * [[:en:1318|1318 AD]] * [[:en:1378|1378 AD]] * [[:en:1438|1438 AD]] * [[:en:1498|1498 AD]] * [[:en:1558|1558 AD]] * [[:en:1618|1618 AD]] * [[:en:1678|1678 AD]] * [[:en:1738|1738 AD]] * [[:en:1798|1798 AD]] * [[:en:1858|1858 AD]] * [[:en:1918|1918 AD]] * [[:en:1978|1978 AD]] | * {{ill|2038 AD|ja|2038年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2038|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2038 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2098 AD|ja|2098年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2098|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2098 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2158 AD|ja|2158年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2158|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2158 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2218 AD|ja|2218年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2218|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2218 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2278 AD|ja|2278年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2278|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2278 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2338 AD|ja|2338年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2338|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2338 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2398 AD|ja|2398年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2398|comm