--> ==Years of Yang Earth Horse== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 58 when divided by 60 is a year of Bokugo ([[:en:Year|year]]). {| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of Bokugo (戊午の年)''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 58|58 AD]] * [[:en:AD 118|118 AD]] * [[:en:178|178 AD]] * [[:en:238|238 AD]] * [[:en:298|298 AD]] * [[:en:358|358 AD]] * [[:en:418|418 AD]] * [[:en:478|478 AD]] * [[:en:538|538 AD]] * [[:en:598|598 AD]] * [[:en:658|658 AD]] * [[:en:718|718 AD]] * [[:en:778|778 AD]] * [[:en:838|838 AD]] * [[:en:898|898 AD]] * [[:en:958|958 AD]] | * [[:en:1018|1018 AD]] * [[:en:1078|1078 AD]] * [[:en:1138|1138 AD]] * [[:en:1198|1198 AD]] * [[:en:1258|1258 AD]] * [[:en:1318|1318 AD]] * [[:en:1378|1378 AD]] * [[:en:1438|1438 AD]] * [[:en:1498|1498 AD]] * [[:en:1558|1558 AD]] * [[:en:1618|1618 AD]] * [[:en:1678|1678 AD]] * [[:en:1738|1738 AD]] * [[:en:1798|1798 AD]] * [[:en:1858|1858 AD]] * [[:en:1918|1918 AD]] * [[:en:1978|1978 AD]] | * {{ill|2038 AD|ja|2038年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2038|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2038 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2098 AD|ja|2098年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2098|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2098 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2158 AD|ja|2158年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2158|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2158 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2218 AD|ja|2218年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2218|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2218 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2278 AD|ja|2278年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2278|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2278 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2338 AD|ja|2338年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2338|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2338 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2398 AD|ja|2398年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2398|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2398 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2458 AD|ja|2458年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2458|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2458 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2518 AD|ja|2518年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2518|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2518 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2578 AD|ja|2578年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2578|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2578 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2638 AD|ja|2638年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2638|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2638 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2698 AD|ja|2698年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2698|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2698 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2758 AD|ja|2758年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2758|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2758 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2818 AD|ja|2818年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2818|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2818 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2878 AD|ja|2878年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2878|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2878 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2938 AD|ja|2938年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2938|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2938 AD|qq=}} * {{ill|2998 AD|ja|2998年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2998|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2998 AD|qq=}} |}
==Months of Yang Earth Horse== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 3 or 8 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|lt=Mizunoto (癸)|2=ja|3=癸|4=zh|5=癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Gui|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoto (癸)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bo|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|lt=Tsuchinoe (戊)|2=ja|3=戊|4=zh|5=戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bo|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:May|May]] is designated as the Bokugo [[:en:Month|Month]]. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the seasonal month (from [[:en:Mangzhong|Mangzhong]] until the day before [[:en:Xiaoshu|Slightly Hot]]) as applicable.
==Days of Yang Earth Horse== The {{ill|selected day|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/selected day|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for Bokugo is as follows. === Selected Day (選日) === Bokugo day is the gap day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}. ==See Also== *{{prefix|qq=}} *{{intitle|qq=}}
